dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2019. [Points representing locations of addresses - points are placed within the parcel with which an address is associated - when possible, points are placed within the footprint of the building with which an address is associated - when a parcel or building is associated with multiple addresses, multiple points will be placed within each parcel or building. - relates to addressable buildings on BUILDING_ID, parcels on TAXKEY, and street centerlines on CLINE_ID.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://gis-mclio.opendata.arcgis.com/
